msgid ""
"We move through the city slowly enough to notice its layers: stone, "
"commerce, devotion, empire, melancholy, reinvention. Streets connect to "
"symbols, buildings to political memory, viewpoints to ways of reading how "
"the city shaped itself over centuries."
msgstr ""

#: landing/templates/viejos/index_django.html:725
msgid ""
"For first-time visitors, it offers orientation with depth. For those "
"returning, it often becomes the moment when Porto begins to make real sense "
"— when the journey becomes memory."
msgstr ""

