#: landing/templates/viejos/index_django.html:759
msgid "History with structure"
msgstr ""

#: landing/templates/viejos/index_django.html:761
msgid ""
"Not a loose collection of anecdotes. A coherent journey through the forces "
"that shaped Porto: religion, commerce, urban form, identity. Each stop "
"carries historical weight and narrative beauty."
msgstr ""

#: landing/templates/viejos/index_django.html:768
msgid "A human pace"
msgstr ""

#: landing/templates/viejos/index_django.html:770
msgid ""
"Small groups, careful rhythm, room for questions. The city has time to "
"appear. You won't be guided — you'll be invited to remember, even what "
"you've never lived."
msgstr ""

#: landing/templates/viejos/index_django.html:777
msgid "A guided reading"
msgstr ""

#: landing/templates/viejos/index_django.html:779
msgid ""
"Architecture, topography, symbols and memory intertwine in a single "
"experience. You leave with orientation, but also with an interpretation — "
"with eyes shining with curiosity."
msgstr ""

#: landing/templates/viejos/index_django.html:790
msgid "Allow yourself a journey with the eyes of someone who sees"
msgstr ""

#: landing/templates/viejos/index_django.html:790
msgid "beyond the facades"
msgstr ""

#: landing/templates/viejos/index_django.html:793
msgid ""
"Some visitors know immediately which walk is theirs. Others prefer to ask "
"first. Both options are welcome — kindness generates kindness."
msgstr ""

